								<!-- bodycontent -->
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">For other uses, see <a href="Philip_Lawrence_(disambiguation)" title="Philip Lawrence (disambiguation)">Philip Lawrence (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<p><b>Philip Ambrose Lawrence</b>, <a href="Queen's_Gallantry_Medal" title="Queen's Gallantry Medal">QGM</a> (21 August 1947<sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup> — 8 December 1995) was a London-based headmaster who was stabbed to death outside the gates of his school when he went to the aid of a pupil who was being attacked by a gang.</p>
